Blin is a simple social network which ia aimed at simplicity
and giving everyone attention. How have we achieved this? We
don't have recommendations system at all. All posts are sorted
by newest ones.

Blin is splitted into blins - a special community, where
everyone can create posts and comment them. You can interpret
it as something like subreddits.

Blin's source code is splitted into two parts - grenki(ru - гренки)
and oladya(ru - оладья). Oladya is Vue 3 frontend and grenki
is Nest backend.

Blin will always be free. It is opensource and every contributor
matters! It is licensed under GNU GPL v3(see LICENSE file for
more details.)

See doc folder for all details you might need.
